tgt: Go down the stairs. Turn right and walk straight until you get to two doors. Turn right on the right door and wait near the chair in the bathroom.

src: exit room walk towards doorway past set of stairs through doorway turn wait in front of sink
tgt: Exit room. Walk towards doorway past the set of stairs. Go through the doorway and turn left. Wait in front of the sink.

tgt: Locate the stove. Travel around the counter to the doorway to the right of the stove. go through the archway and to the stairs. Go up three steps.

src: exit laundry room into kitchen small dining table
tgt: Exit the laundry room and go into the kitchen. Go to the small dining table.

src: walk across patio into house straight past sectional sofa wait near doors
tgt: Walk across the patio and into the house. Go straight past the sectional sofa and wait near the three doors.

src: wait near black chair by bookcase
tgt: Wait near the black chair that is by the bookcase.

src: exit kitchen right past glass table at small wicker chair
tgt: Exit the kitchen. Turn right. Walk past the glass dining table. Stop at the small wicker chair.

src: head hallway right through right side door stop
tgt: Head down the hallway and turn right go through the right side door and stop.

src: enter house right straight into kitchen at end of hall behind first dining chair
tgt: Enter the house and take a right. Go straight into the kitchen at the end of the hall. Stop behind the first dining chair you come to.

src: walk then stair
tgt: walk straight then go up the stair.

src: up stairs wait in hallway
tgt: Walk up the stairs and wait in the hallway.

src: exit bedroom turn inside room at end by guitar
tgt: Exit the bedroom, turn left and wait inside the room at the end, by the guitar.

src: down ladder through trap door on floor turn wait in doorway
tgt: Walk down the ladder through the trap door on the floor. Turn left and wait in the doorway.

src: exit bedroom up stairs then wait on landing by first doorway
tgt: Exit the bedroom and walk up the stairs, then wait on the landing by the first doorway.

src: stairs left on stair landing left through open door on left wait at foot of bed
tgt: Walk up stairs. Make a left on the stair landing. Make a left through the open door on the left. Wait at the foot of the bed.

src: enter house from porch slight left hallway straight room stop by chairs
tgt: Enter house from porch, turn slight left and enter hallway, continue straight  and enter sitting room stop by the chairs.

src: hallway left of stairs turn in room in doorway
tgt: Go to the hallway left of the stairs and turn left in the room. Stop in the doorway.

src: exit bathroom turn past stairs right into ktichen area between kitchen island gray rug
tgt: Exit the bathroom and turn left. Walk past the stairs. Turn right and walk into the ktichen area. Stop between the kitchen island and the gray rug.

src: left stairway right in front of flowers stairs first doorway stop at staircase
tgt: Go left upp the stairway to the right in front of the flowers, go left up the stairs and to the first doorway stop at the staircase.

tgt: turn right enter bedroom go straight then then take left to exit room go straight then stand opposite to mirror.

src: straight towards front door right walk down past sofas recliner stop right before bathroom
tgt: go straight towards the front door and make a right the walk straight down past the sofas and recliner and come to a stop right before the bathroom.

tgt: Walk past thermostat on left. Walk past back of leather sectional on right. Make left after column. Wait at bar stool.

src: exit area head toward kitchen right stairs wait on stair landing after steps
tgt: Exit dinning area, head toward the kitchen, make a right and ascend the stairs, and wait on the stair landing, after two steps.

src: exit bedroom wait at built-in desk in hallway
tgt: Exit the bedroom. Wait at the built-in desk in the hallway.

src: turn right down hallway living room then walk by front doors on first set of stairs
tgt: Turn right and walk down the hallway and enter the living room.  Then walk by the front doors and stop on the first set of stairs.

tgt: Proceed down the hallway away from the bed, pass two leather chairs on your left, a bathroom on your right and stop.

src: stairs right
tgt: go down stairs, turn right.

src: upstairs past couch through dining room wait in entryway near stairs
tgt: Go upstairs, past the couch and through the dining room. Wait in the entryway near the stairs.

tgt: Enter house and turn left. Walk across living room to washing machine and stop.

src: double door on left then right right again right in front of closet entrance
tgt: Go out the double door on your left then turn right and turn right again. Wait right in front of the closet entrance.

src: walk through kitchen right around kitchen island kitchen toward couches wait there
tgt: Walk through the kitchen. Turn right around the kitchen island. Exit the kitchen toward the couches. Wait there.

src: downstairs at level turn stairs halfway stop
tgt: Go downstairs, at the level turn left and go down the stairs halfway and stop.

src: straight pool table then right on last door on right wait at entrance of room
tgt: Go straight. Pass the pool table then go right on the last door on the right and wait at the entrance of that room.

src: walk towards piano through doorway right of piano wait by bench outside of doorway
tgt: Walk towards piano. Go through doorway to the right of piano. Wait by bench outside of doorway.

src: left at door stairs on fifth stair from top
tgt: Take a left at the door, and go up the stairs. Stop on the fifth stair from the top.

src: straight hallway turn wait near beds
tgt: Go straight down the hallway. Turn left and wait near the beds.

tgt: Turn right. Go out the door on your left.  Walk through the bedroom and head straight into the bathroom. Stop in front of the sink.

src: hall turn at end of hall wait in doorway dining room
tgt: Go down the hall and turn left at the end of the hall. Wait in the doorway to the dining room.

tgt: Walk out of the room. Turn left and start going down the stairs. Stop before getting to the bottom.

tgt: Walk towards the pool and then turn left when you get next to it. Turn left and stop in front of the steps to go into the pool.

tgt: Go to the motorcycle. Go to the fire extinguisher. Go to the vice. Go to the thermostat.

src: walk straight toward couches couches steps on stairs ahead
tgt: Walk straight toward the couches. Pass the couches and go up two steps on the stairs straight ahead.

src: stop on doormat of doors room
tgt: Stop on the doormat of the doors to exit this room.

src: turn past countertop forward then right at food shelves turn open door with wooden slats
tgt: Turn left and walk past the countertop. Walk forward then turn right at the food shelves. Turn left and walk open to the door with the wooden slats.

src: exit bedroom turn through door stop
tgt: Exit the bedroom. Turn left, walk through the door, and stop.

src: exit current room left at second door hallway wait at water cooler
tgt: Exit current room, make a left at second door, head down hallway, and wait at water cooler.

tgt: Walk out of the bathroom and turn right into the the bedroom. Turn right and walk into the study. Turn right and walk through the doorway and stop.

src: right walk through bedroom stand in bathroom doorway
tgt: Take a right walk straight through the bedroom and stand in the bathroom doorway.

tgt: Walk straight ahead to the glass door, turn right, walk down the stairs, wait at the bottom of the stairs.

src: inside right at bottom of stairs
tgt: Go inside. Turn right. Stop at the bottom of the stairs.

src: past sinks around corner towards class shelves wait there
tgt: Go past the sinks and around the corner towards some class shelves.  Wait there.

tgt: Walk down the stairs.

tgt: Go left around the corner to make a U turn and go into the small bathroom.

tgt: Walk through the living room area, continuing into the hallway to your right. Down the hall, turn left to wait at the top of the stairs.

tgt: Leave the office and walk straight. Take the first left into the living room. Walk through the  living room onto the patio. Stop once you are on the patio.

tgt: Go towards the table with the vase then turn left and go down the stairs.  Wait at the bottom.

tgt: Exit the bathroom and walk straight past the washer and dryer. Take a hard left in the living room and walk outside to the porch. Wait by the doormat.

tgt: Walk into the bedroom and then walk out of the bedroom and take a right. Walk into the playroom and wait there.

tgt: Walk out of the bedroom, turn right, stop before the stairs.

tgt: Walk to the left of the washer and dryer. Walk past the oven and outside. Turn right and walk onto the patio. Stop just outside the doorway.

tgt: Turn right, enter the house, turn right, wait near the table.

src: exit room left down hall turn out front door there
tgt: exit the room turn the left and walk down the hall. Turn left and walk out the front door.  Stay there.

tgt: Go down both flights of stairs. Walk all the way forward and turn left. Wait in front of the wine room.

tgt: Leave bathroom to bedroom and exit. Wait in hall.

tgt: Exit the room by going through the doorway on the left. Go straight and stop at the top of the stairs.

tgt: Exit the bathroom through the bedroom and into the hallway. Stop and wait near the sliding glass door.

src: walk across area by glass doors pool
tgt: Walk across the sitting area and stop by the sliding glass doors that lead to the pool.

src: down stairs first land wait there near baluster
tgt: Walk down the stairs to the first land and wait there, near the baluster.

tgt: Walk down the stairs, turn right and continue straight into the bedroom. Stop and wait near the doorway.

tgt: Go out of the bedroom and walk into the bedroom next to the video arcade game. In the room take a right and stop in the bathroom doorway.
